name: KillBillies - Feet Drums and Bygones
description:
Debut C.D. by KillBillies!! Get it while stocks last!

Tracklist:
1. I Know You Rider (Trad. Arr: Childs Scott)
2. Blue Paul and Two Reels (Childs, Scott)
3. Rye Whiskey (Punch Brothers. Arr: Childs, Scott)
4. Can't Solve Nothin' (Childs, Scott)
5. Arranmore (Goats Don't Shave. Arr: Childs, Scott)
6. Can't Give Up (Childs, Scott)
7. Raggle Taggle Gypsy Trad. Arr: Childs,Scott)

All instruments played by Ben Childs and Micah Scott.

Recorded by KillBillies at Sonic Sessions, Jupiter, Florida.
